# Portfolio Task  

> A personal portfolio showcasing projects, implemented as part of the GrowthLink internship assignment.

## Task Objectives  
- Build a responsive portfolio website using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
- Deploy the site via GitHub Pages.  
- Demonstrate Git workflow: branching, committing, and pushing to a dedicated repo.

